title: Dakine Sophia Canvas Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2012 Sophia Beach Bag in Bird Love.
Canvas Pack Features:
- Top drawstring closure
- Turn-lock flap closure
- Adjustable web shoulder straps
- Vinyl trims
- Metal hardware
- Exterior zippered pockets
- Interior organizer pockets
- Interior zippered pocket
- Cotton canvas exterior
- Polyester lining
- Black is Crinkle 420D nylon with nylon lining
